class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">7</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">Map &amp; Neighborhoods</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">8</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">Planning Essentials</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">9</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">Expert Advice</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">10</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">Full Directory</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">11</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">Owner &amp; Franchise</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">12</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">FAQs</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">13</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">More Resources</span></button></li></ul></nav><div class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-actions\"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-action-btn toc-action-top\"><i class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 bi bi-arrow-up\"></i>Back to Top</button><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-action-btn\"><i class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 bi bi-arrow-down\"></i>To Bottom</button></div></div></div><main class=\"city-page-layout\"><div class=\"mobile-toc-button\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"mobile-toc-trigger\"><i class=\"bi bi-list-ul\"></i><span>Contents</span></button></div><section id=\"city-hero\" class=\"city-hero-section \"><div class=\"section-shell city-hero-shell\"><div class=\"city-hero-copy\"><div class=\"hero-breadcrumbs\"><a href=\"/\">Home</a><i class=\"bi bi-chevron-right\"></i><span>Dog Parks Directory</span><i class=\"bi bi-chevron-right\"></i><strong>Leesburg</strong></div><p class=\"hero-eyebrow\">Loudoun County Living</p><h1>Dog Parks in Leesburg, VA</h1><p class=\"hero-description\">Discover historic charm and premium off-leash spaces in the heart of Virginia&#x27;s most pet-friendly county. From dedicated runs to expansive nature trails.</p><div class=\"city-rich-description\"><p class=\"rich-description-paragraph\">Leesburg, VA, serves as a premier hub for dog owners in Northern Virginia, balancing its deep historical roots with modern pet infrastructure. The city is anchored by the <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"rich-link\" href=\"https://www.leesburgva.gov/government/departments/parks-recreation/parks/olde-izaak-walton-park\">Leesburg Dog Park</a> at Olde Izaak Walton Park, which provides a well-maintained off-leash environment with separate sections for small and large breeds. For those who prefer scenic exercise, the 1,000-acre <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"rich-link\" href=\"https://www.morvenpark.org\">Morven Park</a> offers an expansive network of trails where dogs can explore the rolling Loudoun County landscape. Our <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"rich-link\" href=\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/states/virginia\">Virginia state directory</a> verifies these locations, reflecting a community culture that treats pets as essential residents.</p><p class=\"rich-description-paragraph\">Navigating local rules is straightforward in Leesburg, provided owners adhere to the strict licensing mandates of Loudoun County. All dogs four months or older must be licensed, a process that ensures up-to-date rabies protection for the entire canine community. Beyond the dedicated runs at <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"rich-link\" href=\"https://www.loudoun.gov/parks\">Creighton West Dog Park</a>, the region is famous for its pet-friendly social scene, including wineries and breweries that welcome leashed companions to join their owners. Whether utilizing our <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"rich-link\" href=\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/owner-resources\">owner resources</a> for training tips or walking the historic brick sidewalks of downtown, Leesburg provides a safe, high-quality environment where every dog can thrive in the heart of Virginia&#x27;s hunt country.</p></div><div class=\"hero-cta-row\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"hero-cta primary\"><i class=\"bi bi-list-check\"></i>Browse directory</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"hero-cta ghost\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i>Open map</button><a class=\"hero-cta text-link\" href=\"/list-your-park\"><i class=\"bi bi-plus-circle\"></i>Submit a park</a></div><div class=\"hero-footnotes\"><span><i class=\"bi bi-sparkles\"></i> <!-- -->Loudoun County standards</span><span><i class=\"bi bi-sparkles\"></i> <!-- -->Dog-friendly wineries nearby</span></div></div><div class=\"city-hero-visual\"><div class=\"hero-image-card\"><img alt=\"Leesburg dog park landscape\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"/images/cities/leesburg/hero.webp\"/><div class=\"hero-image-gradient\"></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"city-premium-section\" aria-labelledby=\"city-premium-heading\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"city-premium-header\"><div><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Premium spotlight</span><h2 id=\"city-premium-heading\">Premium parks in <!-- -->Leesburg</h2><p>Partners highlighted here are currently investing in featured placement across this guide.</p></div><div class=\"city-premium-header-actions\"><a class=\"hero-cta primary\" href=\"/list-your-park\">Feature my park</a><a class=\"hero-cta ghost\" href=\"/contact\">Talk to sales</a></div></div><div class=\"city-premium-values\"><div class=\"city-premium-value-card\"><div class=\"city-premium-value-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-megaphone\"></i></div><h4>Pinned above free listings</h4><p>Premium partners appear before every other card within the city directory.</p></div><div class=\"city-premium-value-card\"><div class=\"city-premium-value-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-envelope-paper\"></i></div><h4>Lead-friendly CTAs</h4><p>Direct website + phone buttons encourage bookings straight from this page.</p></div><div class=\"city-premium-value-card\"><div class=\"city-premium-value-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-clock-history\"></i></div><h4>Always-on exposure</h4><p>Featured cards show even when we haven’t processed new static data yet.</p></div></div><div class=\"city-premium-grid\"><div class=\"city-premium-card animate-pulse\"><div class=\"city-premium-media bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"h-4 w-1/2 rounded bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"mt-2 h-3 w-3/4 rounded bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"mt-4 h-16 rounded bg-slate-100\"></div></div><div class=\"city-premium-card animate-pulse\"><div class=\"city-premium-media bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"h-4 w-1/2 rounded bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"mt-2 h-3 w-3/4 rounded bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"mt-4 h-16 rounded bg-slate-100\"></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"city-insights\" class=\"city-insights-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><section id=\"city-statistics\" class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db city-stats-unified\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stats-section-header\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stats-eyebrow\">City Statistics</span><h2 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db\">How <!-- -->Leesburg<!-- --> stacks up for dog families</h2><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stats-intro\">Verified ratings, review volume, and park availability updated directly from our community directory.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db quick-stats-row\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db quick-stat-card accent\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-tag\">Suburban Freedom</span><h3 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-value\">Wealth of Space</h3><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-copy\">Leesburg provides larger-than-average enclosures compared to urban neighbors, with parks like Olde Izaak Walton setting the standard.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db quick-stat-card \"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-tag\">Nature Focused</span><h3 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-value\">Expansive Trails</h3><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-copy\">With access to over 1,000 acres at Morven Park, local owners have unparalleled options for long-distance trail walking.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db quick-stat-card \"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-tag\">Pet Policy</span><h3 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-value\">No Breed Bans</h3><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-copy\">Loudoun County maintains an inclusive environment with no breed-specific restrictions, fostering a diverse dog community.</p></div></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db amenities-row\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db amenities-header\"><h3 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db\">Most common amenities</h3><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db\">What people are looking for and finding in <!-- -->Leesburg<!-- -->.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db amenities-chips\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db amenity-chip\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chip-percentage\">100<!-- -->%</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chip-label\">Onsite services</span></span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db amenity-chip\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chip-percentage\">1